 time banked the fires of sexy agent  banking the fires of agent  los angeles times p s   wood thomas  nov  movies search overroger moore the new james bond the new bond los angeles times p s   john gavin biography screen actors guild sagaftraorg   zyda joan  sep  dennis weaver seeks actor guild presidency actors guild los angeles times p c   gold aaron  may  tower ticker chicago tribune p b   drake sylvie  sep  will they love lucie too more stage news more stage news more stage news more stage news more stage news los angeles times p m   sullivan dan  sep  local girl makes good in seesaw lucie in seesaw los angeles times p f   colander pat  aug  jerrys just jake with john chicago tribune p b   gavin as grant a test of taste mann roderick los angeles times current file los angeles calif  july  g  bustamante jorge  mar  gavins selection a slap in mexicos face los angeles times p c   a b alan c miller gavin weighs gop bid for us senate  politics the former actor and ambassador meets with leaders who feel the declared candidates cant win los angeles times  august  accessed  november   vernon scott  mar  a look at john gavin at home chicago tribune p d   february   the daily herald from provo utah · page   profile in people magazine  nancy brooks gavin leaving arco to take post at univisa los angeles times  april  accessed  november   business people gavin quits arco for univisa satellite by daniel f cuff and stephen phillips new york times  april  accessed  november   john gavin at biographycom  john gavin biography at americanambassadorsorg  biography at business week accessed  november   hopper hedda  july  laurence olivier shuns  to play caesar chicago daily tribune p b   sam staggs born to be hurt the untold story of imitation of life macmillan  accessed  november   hopper hedda  july  looking at hollywood ski murder film will star john gavin chicago daily tribune p    hopper hedda  january  zugsmiths next big film to be the unvanquished chicago daily tribune p b  