 wrote the treasure of the sierra madre to be shot in mexico biography of simon bolivar   assassination in rome – originally the assassins a chase melodrama to be shot in spain with vittorio gassman cyd charisse and lilo pulver starring gavin as an american newspaperman – gavin pulled out after a disagreement and was replaced by hugh obrian select theatre creditsedit the fantastiks  – pepermille playhouse seesaw  with lucie arnaz – broadway and a tour referencesedit  stars in blue referenced below page  states that gavins mother married ray gavin who adopted john the internet movie data base says that herald ray golenor changed the family name to gavin retrieved february    a b wise james e  rehill anne collier stars in blue movie actors in americas sea services naval institute press p   a b c hopper hedda  july  he never left home los angeles native john gavin wanted no part of pictures so producers beat a path to his door chicago daily tribune p f   richard l coe  june  an artist is at work the washington post times herald p b   a b c joe finnigan  nov  false richboy tag perils film career gavin claims the washington post times herald p g   a b c d e thomas kevin  june  gavin gets down to business los angeles times p d   thomas m pryor special to the new york times  may  universal casts two in new film jane powell george nader to appear in female animal actor replaces gavin new york times p    a b marian christy handsome john gavin reading eagle  august  accessed  december   schallert edwin  july  john gavin wins plum remarque role ford to face doomed world los angeles times p    a b c d e tom donnelly  july  john gavin one for the seesaw john gavin one for the seesaw the washington post p l   scheuer philip k  july  a town called hollywood remarque enjoys adapting own novel into screenplay los angeles times p e   a b thomas m pryor  aug  hollywood ideas newcomers face stardom at universal south pacific on the horizon appraisal pacific launching movie slant new yo